      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=ec2xhsmhp2]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ec2xhsmhp2]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gvflgjt3lh]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gvflgjt3lh]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=mlnobq7ykb]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mlnobq7ykb]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=a9fabjkfdi]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=a9fabjkfdi]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"practicalExamples_Header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/practicalExamples_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762160603822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=327\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/624918545/practicalExamples_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762160603822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"828\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"640024618\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"practicalExamples_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"624918545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"8c5d1792-091f-45cc-bbc7-17dbbbff689c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/practicalExamples_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762160603822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=654 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/practicalExamples_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762160603822&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=327 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"ShadingPracticalLessons-PracticalShadingLessons\"><span data-colorid=\"mlnobq7ykb\">Practical Shading Lessons</span></h1><p>A helpful set of practical shading lessons for you to learn from!</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"cupcake_Header.jpg\" width=\"623\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/cupcake_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762156898084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/624918545/cupcake_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762156898084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"640253968\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"cupcake_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"624918545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"0a85c697-4bb5-48f8-ba01-dd8311e709b4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/cupcake_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762156898084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1246&amp;height=524 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/cupcake_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762156898084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"ShadingPracticalLessons-ShadingACupcake\"><span data-colorid=\"gvflgjt3lh\">Shading A Cupcake</span></h1><p>The Cupcake shading tutorial, brought to you by our friends at Pixar University!</p><p>Coming Soon!</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/393805842/Creating+a+Wooden+Floor\" data-linked-resource-id=\"393805842\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"WoodenFloorboards_header.jpg\" width=\"623\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/624918545/WoodenFloorboards_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762156707041&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=262\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/624918545/WoodenFloorboards_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762156707041&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"640253962\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"WoodenFloorboards_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"624918545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"14\" data-media-id=\"d047a840-7e40-442e-a489-ab45dde64182\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://re